&lt;p&gt;Ex‚ÄëPalantir engineers built &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/181146/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;Meticulous&lt;/a&gt;, an E2E UI testing tool that automatically covers every edge case, boosting product quality and development¬†speed.&lt;/p&gt;
